@node HISTORY "HISTORY"
   WHAT HAS CHANGED FROM VERSION 2.0 REL 1 ?

   1. PROGRAM NOW OPERATES UNDER WORKBENCH 2.0 AND ABOVE NOT JUST 3.0

   2. MENUS OPERATE EASIER

   3. MENU ALARM IF DECOMPRESSION TYPE CHOSEN THAT IS NOT MOUNTED IN
      'C' DIRECTORY OF WORKBENCH

   4. ADDED LHA DECOMPRESSION CAPABILITY.

 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\

   WHAT HAS CHANGED FROM VERSION 2.0 REL 2 ?

   BIG CHANGES FOLKS

   1. ADDED A PREFS TOOL TO ADD DEFS TO ABFDIK SO IT CAN DECOMPRESS
      MANY MORE TYPES OF PROGRAMS.

   2. ADDED A DEFINATION LIST AND LOCATION FILE WHICH SHOULD BE KEPT
      IN THE T DIRECTORY OF YOUR WORKBENCH STARTUP DISK.

   3. ABFDIK NOW WARNS IF DECOMPRESSION TYPE NOT SELECTED.

   4. DECOMPRESSION TYPE NOW DISPLAYED ON MAIN SCREEN.

   5. FIXED DIRECTORY AND ICON CREATION BUTTONS.

   6. DEFAULT MODE IF DEFINATION FILE NOT AVAILABLE.

   7. REDRAWN INTERFACE AND ICONS.

   8. ADDED A FILE IDENTIFICATION ROUTINE IF THE PUBLIC DOMAIN PROGRAM
      CFX PUT INTO YOUR C DIRECTORY.

   9. ADDED A MENU ITEM TURN OFF FEATURE IF YOU TRY AND USE A DECOMPRESSION
      PROGRAM THAT ISN'T IN THE C DIRECTORY.

   10.ADDED ABILITY TO LOAD ANY DEFINATION FILE.

   11.ADDED AN AUTOMATIC FEATURE FOR DMS WITH A QUIT OPTION.

   12.ADDED ABILITY TO DECOMPRESS FILES THAT HAVE AN EXTENSION OTHER
      THAN THE USUAL '.XXX' MEANING A DOT WITH THREE LETTERS AFTER IT.

   13.ADDED ABILITY TO DETECT UNRENAMED DIRECTORIES BEFORE DECOMPRESSION.

   14.FIXED FLASH AT IDLE.

   15.MENU NO LONGER HIDDEN WHEN USING KEY ASSIST OR MENU ASSIST SCREENS.

   16.ONE KEY OPERATION FOR ASSIST SCREENS.

   17.ADDED A READER TO SHOW USER PROGRAMS ALONG WITH EACH DECOMPRESSION
      STRING, VIEWER NAME OR STRING AND ALL EXTENSIONS.

   18.IMPROVED LOG FUNCTION. LOG MUCH MORE INFORMATIVE.

   19.FIXED PRINT UTILITY

   20.ADDED THE ABILITY TO PLAY MODS WHILE DECOMPRESSING

   21.ADDED A GAGUE TO MONITOR THE PROGRAMS TO DECOMPRESS

   22.REMOVED THE CUSTOM EXTENSION OPTION

   23.REMOVED THE ORGANIZE OPTION, NOW ONLY PROGRAMS WITH THE SELECTED
      EXTENSION WILL BE DECOMPRESSED AND MOVED TO THEIR DIRECTORIES.



 \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\

        WHAT HAS CHANGED FROM VERSION 3.0

        ADDED:
        1.  CREATE LIST OF FILES IN SOURCE.
        2.  READ LIST OF FILES IN SOURCE.
        3.  PRINT LIST OF FILES IN SOURCE
        4.  COPY LIST OF FILES TO DESTINATION.
        5.  DELETE LIST OF FILES FROM RAM:.
        6.  SOURCE AND DESTINATION SPACE UPDATER FOR ANY DEVICE.
        7.  MORE WARNINGS ADDED FOR CERTAIN SITUATIONS.
        8.  BUTTON AND MENU HELP UPDATED FOR ADDED ROUTINES.

        FIXED:
        1.  DECOMPRESSION MONITOR WON'T COME ON WHEN AUTO BUTTON PRESSED
            IF SOURCE OR DEST NOT SELECTED.
        2.  SOURCE AND DESTINATION BUTTONS NOW OPERATE MUCH MORE LOGICALLY.

               MENU
        1.  RAM: FILE READER NOW WORKS.
        3.  SOURCE AND DESTINATION MADE CONSISTENT
        3.  PRINTING FILES NOW WORKS





