@node REQUIRED "REQUIREMENTS"
REQUIREMENTS:

    A HARD DRIVE WITH ENOUGH FREE SPACE TO DOWN LOAD AND DECOMPRESS PROGRAMS ON.

    A MINIMUM OF 3 MEGS. YOU MIGHT GET AWAY WITH A TWO MEG MACHINE WITH NOTHING
    ELSE RUNNING, BUT I DON'T RECOMMEND IT, AS THE RAM: IS USED FROM TIME TO TIME
    FOR LIGHT FILE STORAGE.

    WORKBENCH 3.0 OR ABOVE !
    LHA PD archive (included)
    LX  Pd archive (included)
    DMS PD archive (included)
    CFX PD a great file type examiner. (included)
@ENDNODE




